使用在 Ubuntu Linux 分發版內之快倉六套件","/ibus-scj6-ubuntu-1010",{"articles_id":176,"__typename":51},{"id":177,"title":178,"cover_image":179,"summary":184,"slug":185,"__typename":52},"919e15a0-e483-41eb-98c5-fcf7dba450d8","在 Mac OS X 透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法平台使用快倉六",{"id":180,"folder":42,"filename_disk":181,"filename_download":182,"type":158,"description":42,"filesize":183,"__typename":160},"71069a58-654d-4fbb-97aa-a838063a1c0f","71069a58-654d-4fbb-97aa-a838063a1c0f.png","InputSelection.png","167959","此文提供在 Mac OS X 上透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法使用快倉六的方法。","/scj6-mac-yahoo-keykey",{"articles_id":187,"__typename":51},{"id":188,"title":189,"cover_image":190,"summary":195,"slug":196,"__typename":52},"75407dcc-c619-432b-bb5b-21bd10bdbbfd","macOS 快倉六",{"id":191,"folder":42,"filename_disk":192,"filename_download":193,"type":158,"description":42,"filesize":194,"__typename":160},"fead2ca8-c3bc-41ae-a4a2-12527e40df08","fead2ca8-c3bc-41ae-a4a2-12527e40df08.png","Mac-scj6-cin-3.png","55633","繼先前本站文章講述如何透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法使用快倉六後，筆者發現 Mac OS X 10.5 及 10.6 系統本身可以製作自己的輸入法（類似微軟視窗之通用輸入法）。","/scj6-macos",{"articles_id":198,"__typename":51},{"id":199,"title":200,"cover_image":201,"summary":206,"slug":207,"__typename":52},"a1a783bc-7f41-4df1-8284-14b7969a0199","在 MeeGo 使用快倉六",{"id":202,"folder":42,"filename_disk":203,"filename_download":204,"type":158,"description":42,"filesize":205,"__typename":160},"a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf","a88d0d1c-9f56-4e1f-a1b5-de000c44baaf.png","MeeGo-Screenshot-1.png","62490","本文講述如何在 MeeGo 1.0 for Netbooks 安裝及使用快速倉頡第六代中文輸入法。","/scj6-meego",{"articles_id":209,"__typename":51},{"id":210,"title":211,"cover_image":212,"summary":217,"slug":218,"__typename":52},"7fa853ed-8edc-402e-b34e-402e1fad1585","用於 Nokia N900 maemo 之快倉六",{"id":213,"folder":42,"filename_disk":214,"filename_download":215,"type":158,"description":42,"filesize":216,"__typename":160},"3e1f08e4-6982-4d49-99ae-fd3405731d8c","3e1f08e4-6982-4d49-99ae-fd3405731d8c.png","maemo-scj6.png","1059730","用於 maemo mscim 之快倉六軟件","/scj6-maemo",{"articles_id":220,"__typename":51},{"id":221,"title":222,"cover_image":42,"summary":42,"slug":223,"__typename":52},"b0badc5e-272e-463f-ba01-59aad7d15d13","相關網站","/related-links",{"articles_id":225,"__typename":51},{"id":226,"title":227,"cover_image":42,"summary":228,"slug":132,"__typename":52},"16f388f4-5324-4377-80a3-e8ddd8995875","快速倉頡輸入法第六代","快速倉頡輸入法第六代（快倉六）是一個多功能和多任務的輸入法系統。在功能方面，它不但擁有多種不同版本的倉頡輸入法、速成輸入法、廣東話輸入法、高效率的標點、特殊符號和數字編碼、日文編碼、香港政府三千常用字編碼、簡碼和容錯碼。",{},1692184037339]